Requirements for deployment:

	- use deploy/deploy.py 
		python deploy/deploy.py -xf -v 1

	- npm (https://npmjs.org/)
		curl https://npmjs.org/install.sh | sudo bash

	- nodejs
		sudo aptitude install nodejs

	- ruby (1.8-dev on ubuntu)
	- rubygems (1.8)
		sudo aptitude install ruby1.8-dev rubygems
		sudo gem install rubygems-update
